@page
@model sourcestack1.Pages.Password.ForgetModel
@{
}
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class=" col-4">
            <h2 style="margin-top :80px;margin-bottom :20px; font-size :30px">
                (｡ŏ_ŏ) 忘了
            </h2>
            <hr />
            <nav style=" border:1px dashed;border-color:gainsboro ;margin-top:20px">
                <div class="nav nav-tabs" id="nav-tab" role="tablist">
                    <a class="nav-item nav-link active" id="nav-home-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#nav-home" role="tab"
                       aria-controls="nav-home" aria-selected="true" style="margin-right:5px">
                        <span class="fa fa-lock"></span>密码
                    </a>
                    <a class="nav-item nav-link" id="nav-profile-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#nav-profile" role="tab"
                       aria-controls="nav-profile" aria-selected="false" style="margin-right:5px">
                        <span class=" fa fa-user-circle-o"></span>
                        用户名
                    </a>
                </div>
            </nav>
            <div class="tab-content" id="nav-tabContent">
                <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="nav-home" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-home-tab">
                    <form>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="formGroupExampleInput">Email：（* 必填）</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="formGroupExampleInput" placeholder="注册时填写的Email地址">
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <div class="input-group ">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="必须全称，且不要忘了点击 搜索 按钮"
                               aria-label="Recipient's username" aria-describedby="basic-addon2">
                        <div class="input-group-append">
                            <span class="input-group-text" id="basic-addon2"><span class="fa fa-search"></span></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="exampleInputcaptcha">验证码:(必填）</label>
                        <div>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control d-inline " id="exampleInputcaptcha" style="width :100px" size="4">
                            <span></span>
                            <span style="margin-left :5px">点击输入框显示</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">提交</button>
                    <button type="reset" class=" btn btn-light">重置</button>
                </div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="nav-profile" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="nav-profile-tab">
                    <div class="input-group ">
                        <label for="exampleInputcaptcha">QQ：</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" aria-label="Recipient's username" aria-describedby="basic-addon2">
                        <div class="input-group-append">
                            <span class="input-group-text" id="basic-addon2">
                                <span class=" fa fa-search"></span>
                                查找
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group mb-3">
                        <label for="exampleInputcaptcha">Email：</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" aria-label="Recipient's username" aria-describedby="basic-addon2">
                        <div class="input-group-append">
                            <span class="input-group-text" id="basic-addon2">
                                <span class=" fa fa-search"></span>
                                查找
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-5 offset-2 ">
            <aside>
                <h3 class="text-info " style="margin-bottom :10px">
                    <i class="fa fa-question-circle" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size :1.5rem"></i>
                    说明
                </h3>
                <ol>
                    <li><p>重置密码的邮件会发送到你填写的Email中。</p></li>
                    <li><p>输入用户名之后，还要点击旁边的 <span class=" fa fa-search">按钮</span> ，以完成Email地址的填写。</p></li>
                    <li><p>现目前，还没有针对未激活Email做特殊提示，请务必确保Email正确。</p></li>
                </ol>
            </aside>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>